& [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioCorpusLaunchQueue001] is the active semantic stack frame for the diversified LM Studio corpus launch queue
  + [frame_id] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_corpus_launch_queue_001
  + [frame_state] is active
